node.text:
Rawsome day guys!⁣
⁣
Are you starting to run out of juice working from home? I've got your back⁣
⁣
Mougou's Products include Cold Pressed Juice and Nut Milk. Freshly made to order with no preservatives nor artificial sweetener.⁣
⁣
Their menu has a great deal of choices and here are the top 4 I've tried!⁣
⁣
√ 𝐍𝐎 𝐖𝐎𝐑𝐑𝐈𝐄𝐒: Kale, Celery, Green Apple and Lemon 👑 (Must try!)⁣⁣
Soothes nerves, detoxifies and promotes better sleep quality.⁣
⁣
√ 𝐈𝐂𝐘 𝐎𝐍𝐆𝐋𝐀𝐈 𝐘𝐎𝐔: Pineapple, Cucumber, Pear and Fresh Mint (best served with ice to amplify the mint) ⁣
Aids in the digestion and absorption of proteins which is crucial for building muscles.⁣
⁣
√ 𝐍𝐔𝐓𝐄𝐋𝐋𝐀: Hazelnut, unsweetened Cocoa Powder, H2O, Sea Salt, Medjool Dates ⁣
Reduces the risk of cancers, cardiovascular disease, and accelerates your metabolism.⁣
⁣
√ 𝐎𝐍𝐄 𝐈𝐍 𝐀 𝐌𝐄𝐋𝐎𝐍: Honey Melon, Watermelon and Carrot ⁣
Rich in minerals such as Beta-Carotine and potassium which promotes healthy vision, bones, immune system and reproduction. ⁣
⁣
Mougou focus on keeping the mixture simple to ensure maximum benefits deliver from each ingredient. Most juices include 4 to 7 different fresh ingredients.⁣
⁣
My favourite got to be their 'no worries' because you can taste the extracts of the green vegetables and fruits. Yet so nice and refreshing to drink it. Exceptionally good for those who might be having sleepless night or stress!⁣
⁣
What's best? They also offer Daily Juice Cleanse pack that helps detoxifies and reset your body!⁣
⁣
🅿🆁🅸🅲🅴🆂⁣

⁣
